name: DOITcoin
description:
DOITCoin was born as a project that seeks to satisfy the need of
people who are transitioning into the world of cryptocurrencies that
have to do many transactions to buy / sell / buy / buy / sell coins to
get to buy a product in real life.
We through $DOIT want to achieve that people who buy $DOIT in
the future can use our currency and other cryptocurrencies to buy
products online.
